{"tid":1671845,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[加泰集會] [Assembly] [集思廣益] 唔想運動輸既同我入黎！ 不分化不割席補救Post [中/Eng]","createTime":"2019-10-23T17:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:16:02.000Z","uid":103618,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fec30cc48b52dd266181cc14782d0f3aa91170b9","tid":1671845,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:38:29.000Z","msg":"【借人地帳號Po】<br />\n<br />\n呢個Post係用黎討論下<ins>聽日既集會點樣變得對我地有利</ins>，減低潛在負面影響&mdash;&mdash;姐係補救措施<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係分析去唔去。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">集會利弊分析／背景資料既POST會放係最下面大家自己禁／自行判斷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一句 講晒<br />\n去既係出於<ins>針對警暴既立場</ins>（維護普世價值／唔好當人地係condom仔）<br />\n唔去既係出於<ins>個人戰略考慮</ins>（唔係最好時機／唔好比位人入）<br />\n<br />\n因為大家各有睇法，去或唔去都有既道理，甘問題黎啦，集會照常舉行，但係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點樣做先唔會比炒作份子亂帶風向，令隱憂成真+手足之間進一步分化？</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共既垃圾一向唔需要理會，而家重點擺<ins>外媒</ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">在場和理非 + 網上宣傳非常重要 </span></strong></div><br />\n我地一切「補救」措施，係同一個目的：務求令聽日集中係<span style=\"color: green;\">人權/人道處理示威</span>， <span style=\"color: maroon;\">唔好扯上加泰獨立</span><br />\n小弟愚見如下：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1）文宣／標語牌<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須扣題</span></span><br />\n學立場話齋，我地要<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">- 呼籲西班牙政府和平處理加泰示威<br />\n- 譴責西班牙警察暴力對待示威者<br />\n- 強調香港人堅持捍衛人權、自由等普世價值</span><br />\n唔好齋舉 #StandWithCatalonia 等等但係咩都唔解釋&mdash;&mdash;越係用字模糊越係比對家胡亂詮釋既空間。記住，<ins>一定要畫出腸講明大家為exactly乜野集氣</ins>。<br />\n例如 呼籲 唔好學中共／港共鎮壓手法； 提醒 佢地係<strong>西方民主社會</strong>，（學阿爺既講法）要「堅決維護西方核心價值」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者<br />\n#POLICE BRUTALITY <br />\n#Don&rsquo;t Learn from CCP<br />\n#Do things the right way<br />\n之類，大家有更好既建議歡迎提出。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2）<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分散</span>媒體注意</span><br />\n一係直接黎個分享會講埋其他地方警暴問題／如果有人舉獨旗，唔該幫手舉埋其他國旗或者咩都好，變成全球反警暴又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係直接大量宣傳11月2日既維園集會，因為我地都需要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳見<br />\n目標100萬人！11.2 「求援國際 堅守自治 」流水式維園集會！英美加澳日 全球同步聲援！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671328</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟係度拋磚引玉，有咩提議請務必攞出黎討論，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">再重申一次，我地係黎聲援去既手足，補番任何不足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同意既請幫手推上熱門，我地得番幾個鐘咋屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n==============================<br />\n背景資料：<br />\n[掃盲]加泰羅利亞懶人包 feat. 應唔應該推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656410</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n去定唔去：<br />\n【文長慎入】加泰事件 &mdash; 論獨立思考及運動發展<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671453</a><br />\n<br />\n【請集中討論】香港加泰人權自由集會籌委會正式聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671373</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞：<br />\n周四加泰人權自由集會 獲發不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E7%8D%B2%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yFRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=6bd1d4db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%258D%25B2%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%2580%259A%25E7%259F%25A5%25E6%259B%25B8%2F&h=b6b5575f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9B%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9B%86%E6%9C%83-%E7%8D%B2%E7%99%BC%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E6%9B%B8/</a>"},{"pid":"86398105608ebe80fc9929cab3d1f18da62d489e","tid":1671845,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:48:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>I will now recap in English</strong><br />\n<br />\nThis post aims at discussing <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>HOW NOT TO FUCK UP THE ASSEMBLY AND THE MOVEMENT</strong>, NOT TO DISCUSS WHETHER OR NOT YOU SHOULD GO.</span></span><br />\n<br />\nIn short, you participate because of the values (no police brutality), you don&rsquo;t due to strategic concerns. <br />\n<br />\nWhatever choice you make, the Assembly is still gonna happen tomorrow.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: left;\">SO WHAT DO WE DO?</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">1) MAKE SURE TO FOCUS ON THE ASPECTS THAT ECHOS WITH HONG KONG PROTESTS, i.e. POLICE BRUTALITY</span></strong></em><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: blue;\">2) STAY AWAY FROM THE CONTROVERSIAL ASPECTS (i.e. Independence) BECAUSE IT&rsquo;S NOT OUR PLACE TO SAY SHIT</span></em></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Online (Digital Pamphlets, Twitter/Reddit): </span><br />\nWhether you&rsquo;re gonna create new hashtags or posters, do whatever you can to make sure tomorrow&rsquo;s assembly is <strong>ONLY ASSOCIATED WITH CORE VALUES</strong><br />\n<br />\nSome ideas: #DoNotLearnFromCCP #PoliceBrutality<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">On-site billboards: </span><br />\n<ins>Be as explicit as possible </ins>with your wordings. Write EXACTLY what we are concerned about, <strong>NO AMBIGUOUS WORDINGS</strong> (please do not only write &lsquo;stand with catalonia&rsquo;) or else those mother fuckers can spin many wild stories.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Better yet, promote our upcoming demonstration on 2 November!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標100萬人！11.2 「求援國際 堅守自治 」流水式維園集會！英美加澳日 全球同步聲援！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1671328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1671328</a><br />\n<br />\nAny other suggestions or comments? We only have a few hours left till &ldquo;crunch time&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b009e79af45692ae4e74411c084662b75542a7e","tid":1671845,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"自推10次 1/10"},{"pid":"7b7b6cf4e790fbd3863c2248ace8a61eb5fd778b","tid":1671845,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"自推10次 2/10"},{"pid":"57f874e6a5cbfba694a8fd10bf6027da34958706","tid":1671845,"uid":103618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T17:50:02.0